## Manual Trace — `[1,1,3]` and `[2,3,4]`

| Step | l1 | l2 | Pick | Result so far |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | 1 | 2 | l1 (1 < 2) | 1 |
| 2 | 1 | 2 | l1 (1 < 2) | 1 → 1 |
| 3 | 3 | 2 | l2 (2 < 3) | 1 → 1 → 2 |
| 4 | 3 | 3 | l1 (equal, <=) | 1 → 1 → 2 → 3 |
| 5 | None | 3 → 4 | attach remaining l2 | 1 → 1 → 2 → 3 → 3 → 4 |

